As Jared mentioned, some of the words are duplicated.

00:00:11.582 --> 00:00:13.290
You know, we'll try to condense those and

00:00:13.290 --> 00:00:15.630
just have one copy of each of the words.

00:00:15.630 --> 00:00:20.949
Some words share the same stem, for example, pile and piles.

00:00:22.270 --> 00:00:24.630
